<p align="center" style="text-align: center;"><span><span><span><span><span>山东省公安特巡警举行实战技能比武竞赛<span><span><span><span><span>（央广网发 通讯员崔前程 供图</span></span></span></span></span>）</span></span></span></span></span></p>
